59.heading: Nash, Danny.
59.title: "Murder Mansion" 8 p. in Adventures into Darkness, no. 5
59.author: [No author]
notes: Summary (by Ryan Claytor): A blackmail operation goes wrong when Danny and Helen Nash shoot and kill a client. They hide in an abandoned brownstone owned by a Mr. Sylvestre, who is supposedly away in Florida. Finding an old book in the house's library, Danny reads a passage which summons Teneshad, a demon from the half-world, who proclaims himself to be a slave to his conjurors. Teneshad eventually traps the couple in the house. Helen escapes into the arms of policemen who search the place, unable to find any sign of Danny or Teneshad. It is then revealed that Teneshad has hidden Danny in a soundproof cellar, where Mr. Sylvestre is also tied up and begging for death.
